{"tid":203104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓自爆冇人提？","createTime":"2017-04-16T04:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T06:32:19.000Z","uid":25673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"929f21cead3865d13d72abe98930ac1436543ef8","tid":203104,"uid":25673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:55:51.000Z","msg":"南韓軍方指北韓早上再次試射導彈，結果失敗。南韓聯合參謀本部說，北韓早上在東部海岸城巿新浦，試射一枚未知類型的導彈，以失敗告終。美國軍方說，導彈在發射時爆炸，暫時未確定導彈型號。<br />\n<br />\n北韓在昨日太陽節舉行盛大閱兵儀式，首次展示潛射彈道導彈，及多款長中短程導彈，但並未如外界推測，試射導彈或核試。"},{"pid":"8b0f3c2d1a1e3de28042476501780cded6dcce0d","tid":203104,"uid":33728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:56:47.000Z","msg":"自爆"},{"pid":"cbad544c270cc747f567f62a1abc87b322da2aeb","tid":203104,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c646c0458b56cdf8953fed3376cb38e39845a9","tid":203104,"uid":35248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T05:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb9438f51fd25d6b3f1ab1191f708e465ced1d5","tid":203104,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T06:17:08.000Z","msg":"負責將領俾人拎左去炮決未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b27f05395f96b83b528b20a33e6a05aa4366885","tid":203104,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T06:21:13.000Z","msg":"英國研究<br />\n中國製造<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">北韓發射</span>"},{"pid":"11b3848d2e0808229827aafb6b203b67a1a8f6ec","tid":203104,"uid":89411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T06:32:04.000Z","msg":"廢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58ac72a7a890fab53c8d27afe1691f1f747f845","tid":203104,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T06:32: